 library based on the 2015 version of ENSDF.                      1323 1451
 ENDF formatting enabled                                          1323 1451
 Exclusive emission from CN and target enabled                    1323 1451
 Exclusive spectra available for residues distant                 1323 1451
   from CN up to 2 neut. or 2 prot.                               1323 1451
 Target excited to the level # 2                                  1323 1451
 EMPIRE-specific level densities (J>>K aprox.)                    1323 1451
 HRTW width fluctuation correction calculated  up to  3.00 MeV    1323 1451
 Exciton model calculations with code PCROSS                      1323 1451
 Cluster emission in terms of the Iwamoto-Harada model            1323 1451
 Kalbach systematics angular distributions (see RIPL-1)           1323 1451
 Mean free path parameter in PCROSS set to  1.5 (Recomm:~1.5)     1323 1451
 CN anisotropy calculated using Blatt-Biedenharn coefficients     1323 1451
 CN decay and Direct cross sections added incoherently            1323 1451
 Traditional Hauser-Feschbach Tlj_{CC}(E)=Tlj_{GS}(E-Egs)         1323 1451
 E1 strength function set to RIPL MLO1                            1323 1451
 GDR parameters from RIPL/Exp.data+Plujko systematics             1323 1451
 Gamma-transition multipolarity set to    2                       1323 1451
